aws_services: VPC, EC2, RDS, S3, Auto Scaling, Route 53, CloudWatch, IAM, Secrets Manager, NAT Gateway, Internet Gateway, AWS WAF, AWS Backup
background: Comprehensive cloud environment setup with VPC, Auto Scaling, RDS Multi-AZ, S3, WAF, Route 53, VPC Flow Logs, and AWS Backup. Model initially provided fixed EC2 instances, single NAT Gateway, and missing several AWS services. IDEAL_RESPONSE implements full enterprise-grade architecture with high availability, security best practices, and disaster recovery.
